    <li><strong>✅ Fast, Flexible Scheduling:</strong> Appliance issues can throw off your entire routine. That’s why we offer same-day or next-day appointments whenever possible and always respect your time.</li>
    <li><strong>✅ Upfront Pricing & Honest Service:</strong> Before any work begins, you’ll receive a clear and detailed estimate—no hidden fees, no unexpected charges. Just honest, professional service from start to finish.</li>
